@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fczues(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = 0.81
    v1 = tmp
    v2 = v0
    v2 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.96 / v1 + 0.02)) / ((v0 + 0.76 / v1 + 0.66) * tmp))
    v0 = 0.84
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs((v1 + wp.sin(v2 + 0.29)))
    data[tid] = v0
